latestIgtvVideos.title: FIRST IMPRESSIONS EP : 05
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Wow SkinScience x Meghana Vora 
Have you ever heard of sunscreen face serum? 
Meet my new best friend from wow skin science with SPF 35 and a matte finish.. Yes you heard that right!
@wowskinscienceindia 
Has launched a new serum which has the goodness of sunscreen so it means you don’t have to buy any new serum or an additional sunscreen in your skincare routine. This sunscreen face serum works as a two in one ingredient, acts as a sunscreen and face serum isn’t that fantastic?
It also has goodness of 
- raspberry extracts
- Avocado oil
- carrot seed extract
How to use it?
Apply a small amount on cleansed and tone face and neck. Massage well. And top it up with moisturiser.
It also has various benefits like
- It’s Non Greasy
- Protects the skin from harmful sun rays that is UVA and UVB.
- I definitely rated a 9 on 10
- If you have any skin issues I recommend you to do a patch test before directly apply it on to your skin.
You can revert back if with your queries and any other questions that you might have & her I’d be happy to help you! 
.
.
.
You can buy it from www.buywow.in 
.
.

latestIgtvVideos.title: FIRST IMPRESSIONS EP: 04
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Wow Skin Science X Meghana Vora 
Tried out @wowskinscienceindia Activated Charcoal Peel Off Mask and believe me it worked perfectly fine for me. 
I'd definitely get 10/10 for this one. 
.
.
The packaging is fine, it also comes with an applicator and apply it evenly on the face!
Let it dry for 20 mins and then gently peel it off. 
It suits all skin types but in the box, they  have mentioned to avoid using it on inflammatory skin tone. 
If you feel burning sensation for 2 mins it is fine, no need to worry but if the the sensation lasts long please wash your face. 
.
.
You can buy from www.buywow.in 
Or check on nykaa!
.
.
